      "author_association": "NONE",
      "body": "Concept ACK,\r\nI suggest adding this conndition at \r\nhttps://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/a7c30da1f6fc2eebd7514dd032fbb54940d467de/src/net_processing.cpp#L4823 \r\nSo the bitcoin client will not respond to any **GETADDR** message from a feeler connection or outbound connections\r\n```\r\nif (!pfrom.IsInboundConn() || pfrom.IsFeelerConn()) {\r\n            LogDebug(BCLog::NET, \"Ignoring \\\"getaddr\\\" from %s connection. peer=%d\\n\", pfrom.ConnectionTypeAsString(), pfrom.GetId());\r\n            return;\r\n}\r\n```\r\n",
      "user": {
        "login": "taki-abedesselam",
        "id": 25395597,
        "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjI1Mzk1NTk3",
        "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/25395597?v=4",
